title: Succombe Qui Doit (2014) (Scanlation) (phillywilly-Vee) cbr
description:
A robbery that went wrong...
Hiding out in a scrapyard, four young criminals take Jose Marchado hostage, the boss of the place, a strong, silent type from who knows where.
How can they escape the police dragnet? Save the wounded man? And, most of all, deliver the proceeds of the robbery to their boss, the sinister La Villette?
An expressionist work filled with violence and an uncommon harshness,Succombe qui doit revisits the eternal motifs of the noir novel with panache.
